"The Quest".

2
00:00:03,760 --> 00:00:05,520
The first part of this episode is...

3
00:00:06,520 --> 00:00:09,480
Miyagawa Expedition,
the 14th edition.

4
00:00:09,560 --> 00:00:13,120
This time, you'll explore Amami
Islands in Kagoshima Prefecture.

5
00:00:13,200 --> 00:00:14,200
Amami Islands?

6
00:00:14,280 --> 00:00:15,720
Like Amami Oshima?

7
00:00:15,800 --> 00:00:20,160
Amami Islands are located between
the mainland of Kyushu and Okinawa.

8
00:00:20,240 --> 00:00:22,880
They have a subtropical climate,

9
00:00:22,960 --> 00:00:25,360
and are home to rare plants
and animals,

10
00:00:25,440 --> 00:00:26,840
including endemic species.

11
00:00:26,920 --> 00:00:29,760
It's an unexplored region
with its own ecosystem.

12
00:00:30,280 --> 00:00:32,720
There are two things
that we want to find.

13
00:00:32,800 --> 00:00:35,680
To find the legendary endangered
animal, the Amami rabbit.

14
00:00:35,760 --> 00:00:37,280
I've heard of them.

15
00:00:37,360 --> 00:00:40,080
But I've, of course, never seen
them, because they're legendary.

16
00:00:40,160 --> 00:00:43,520
Another one is a mysterious cave
in the depth of the earth.

17
00:00:43,600 --> 00:00:45,440
You love caves, don't you?

18
00:00:45,520 --> 00:00:47,640
We went to a cave before, didn't we?

19
00:00:47,720 --> 00:00:49,520
The golden cave in Thailand.

20
00:00:49,600 --> 00:00:51,440
It was grey.

21
00:00:51,520 --> 00:00:54,520
You told me we'd no longer
visit caves.

22
00:00:54,600 --> 00:00:57,920
In the back of the cave, there are
stalactites on terraced fields.

23
00:00:58,000 --> 00:01:00,160
Terraced fields? Are you sure?

24
00:01:00,240 --> 00:01:01,880
I'm a bit worried.

25
00:01:02,280 --> 00:01:05,080
This time, we'll visit two islands
of Amami Islands,

26
00:01:05,160 --> 00:01:10,640
and capture Amami rabbit
and the mysterious cave on camera.

27
00:01:10,720 --> 00:01:13,880
A new member wants to join
this expedition.

28
00:01:14,880 --> 00:01:16,000
What?

29
