Here I am.

30
00:01:17,360 --> 00:01:18,520
It's Okasan.

31
00:01:18,600 --> 00:01:21,560
It's Assistant Director Hirata,
also known as Okasan.

32
00:01:21,640 --> 00:01:24,360
Who first started
calling you Okasan?

33
00:01:24,440 --> 00:01:27,240
Mr Degawa was the first one
who called me by that name.

34
00:01:27,320 --> 00:01:28,720
That's how it started.

35
00:01:28,800 --> 00:01:30,400
What do you think of that?

36
00:01:30,480 --> 00:01:31,520
I feel honoured.

37
00:01:31,600 --> 00:01:33,200
You feel honoured?

38
00:01:33,280 --> 00:01:36,040
What was your very first nickname?

39
00:01:36,120 --> 00:01:37,840
Himiko.

40
