535
00:22:21,160 --> 00:22:23,280
- What?
- What?

536
00:22:23,360 --> 00:22:25,000
It looks creepy.

537
00:22:25,080 --> 00:22:27,760
The entrance is already difficult
to get past.

538
00:22:27,840 --> 00:22:30,800
It's already very tight.
