539
00:22:30,880 --> 00:22:32,680
It looks crazy.

540
00:22:32,760 --> 00:22:36,600
They crawl on all fours
for 20 metres in a river.

541
00:22:36,680 --> 00:22:38,520
I've never done this before.

542
00:22:38,600 --> 00:22:40,560
Crawling itself is quite hard.

543
00:22:40,640 --> 00:22:45,320
