600
00:25:13,600 --> 00:25:15,400
And...

601
00:25:15,480 --> 00:25:17,040
Wow, it's so white.

602
00:25:18,040 --> 00:25:20,520
This is the best viewpoint.

603
00:25:20,600 --> 00:25:23,320
It's a completely different colour.
I've never seen it before.

604
00:25:24,080 --> 00:25:26,040
I've never seen this before.

605
00:25:26,520 --> 00:25:29,000
Glossy stalactites
in a pure white colour,

606
00:25:29,080 --> 00:25:31,560
and completely transparent water.

607
00:25:31,640 --> 00:25:32,880
Incredible.

608
00:25:32,960 --> 00:25:37,320
They will instal about
30 white lights in this area.

609
00:25:37,760 --> 00:25:40,120
Here's the view.

610
00:25:41,120 --> 00:25:42,800
I'll look now.

611
00:25:43,960 --> 00:25:46,080
It's beautiful!

612
00:25:46,160 --> 00:25:48,680
It's such a beautiful cave.

613
00:25:49,360 --> 00:25:54,200
It's a series of terraced
stalactite pools,

614
00:25:55,200 --> 00:25:58,640
which is 50 metres long
and 30 metres wide.

615
00:25:58,720 --> 00:26:03,080
A mystical scenery that exists
underground of a tropical island.

616
00:26:03,160 --> 00:26:06,920
These pools are so pretty!

617
00:26:07,000 --> 00:26:09,240
- This is quite rare, isn't it?
- Yes.

618
00:26:09,320 --> 00:26:12,200
They line up like a paillette,

619
00:26:12,280 --> 00:26:13,880
