621
00:26:18,280 --> 00:26:20,400
On this day,
there was plenty of water,

622
00:26:20,480 --> 00:26:23,720
and according to the guide,
it was the perfect condition.

623
00:26:23,800 --> 00:26:24,720
That's great.

624
00:26:24,800 --> 00:26:27,280
Chappu, Okasan, are you okay?

625
00:26:27,360 --> 00:26:28,480
Yes.

626
00:26:28,560 --> 00:26:33,920
Ginsuido was formed
over millions of years.

627
00:26:34,000 --> 00:26:38,720
After a rough journey,
the expedition members

